sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Middleware
    participant BrandSignInPage
    participant BrandSignInForm
    participant Clerk
    participant BrandDashboard

    User->>Middleware: Navigates to /sign-in/brand
    
    alt is user already authenticated?
        alt role === "brand"
            Middleware-->>User: redirect to /brand
        else role === "influencer"
            Middleware-->>User: redirect to /influencer
        end
    else no session
        Middleware->>BrandSignInPage: render BrandSignInPage
        BrandSignInPage->>BrandSignInForm: renders BrandSignInForm
    end
    
    User->>BrandSignInForm: Fills: email, password
    User->>BrandSignInForm: Clicks Sign in → handleSignIn fires
    BrandSignInForm->>Clerk: signIn.create({ identifier: email, password })
    
    alt error
        Clerk-->>BrandSignInForm: returns error
        BrandSignInForm-->>User: toast.error shown, flow ends
    else status === "complete"
        Clerk-->>BrandSignInForm: returns complete
        BrandSignInForm->>Clerk: setActive({ session: createdSessionId })
        Note over BrandSignInForm, Clerk: Session active in browser
        BrandSignInForm->>User: router.push("/brand")
        
        User->>Middleware: intercepts /brand request
        Middleware->>Middleware: checks: userId exists ✓
        Middleware->>BrandDashboard: forwards to layout
        BrandDashboard->>BrandDashboard: layout checks: role === "brand" ✓
        BrandDashboard-->>User: Access granted → dashboard renders
    end
